13
00:01:29,055 --> 00:01:37,289
[Melody of Golden Age]

14
00:01:37,289 --> 00:01:41,224
[Episode 4]

15
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:01,200
Morning, Great Chief.

16
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,600
It's not morning anymore.

17
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,040
It seems that

18
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,600
the Ministry of Justice
is not very strict in rules.

19
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:09,080
Thanks to you.

20
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:12,480
I slept so well last night.

21
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,280
You said the second branch
of the Liang family is not the murderer.

22
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:18,280
How certain are you?

23
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:21,040
Almost certain.

24
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:22,680
Go on then.

25
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,200
Now your head

26
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:26,840
is still on your neck

27
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,240
If I keep staying up all night like this,

28
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,800
even with a head,

29
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,240
I would still have to go to underworld.

30
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:34,504
My lord.

31
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,640
My lord, Madam.

32
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:39,240
Time for breakfast.

33
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,320
I have no appetite.

34
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,480
Wow.

35
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:50,720
What a mess.

36
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,760
Yan Xing.

37
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,520
Liuniang.

38
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,760
Chuichui.

39
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:07,040
Seriously?

40
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:09,360
Doesn't the Shen Mansion provide you meals?

41
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,640
- If I eat with him,
- She's still alive.

42
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:13,440
- I'm afraid I'll choke.
- Looks like she's fine. Let's go.

43
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:15,200
Choke?

44
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,480
No way.

45
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,680
I heard that you and White Ghost

46
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,520
are very much in love.

47
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,000
A good Jack

48
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,080
makes a good Jill.

49
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:25,600
I've heard all about
you two riding a horse together.

50
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,640
Tell me the truth.

51
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:30,480
Indeed, good news stays within,

52
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:32,320
but bad news spreads far and wide.

53
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,680
Bad news?

54
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,600
You're now famous
among the circle of noblewomen

55
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,560
in the Imperial City.

56
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,920
Back then, there was a woman
who feigned fainting

57
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,520
and fell into Shen Du's arms.

58
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,160
And she got arrested by the Imperial Guards

59
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,160
and sentenced for

60
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:46,680
the crime of offending the Great Chief.

61
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,720
It really is his style.

62
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,080
Since then,

63
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,240
once the women in Xiang'an City

64
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,560
see White Ghost,

65
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,200
they'd avoid him.

66
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,120
I can't believe he would
show affection with you in the street

67
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:58,920
and had close contact.

68
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:01,480
It's better to have less contact.

69
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:12,584
This is…

70
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,240
On the night of your wedding,

71
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,640
Ming Hall was on fire.

72
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,160
The Empress Dowager was furious.

73
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,120
Several people from the Imperial Guards
were held accountable.

74
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:23,360
Even your husband was fined his salary.

75
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:25,760
I didn't know that.

76
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:28,920
I heard about that poor scholar
named Chen Baiyi.

77
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:31,360
He set himself on fire in the Ming Hall

78
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:33,440
because he sought fame but failed.

79
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,680
He is dead.

80
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,280
His family should have been implicated.

81
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:38,120
But…

82
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,280
only this nearly sixty-year-old,

83
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,640
blind and deaf old lady

84
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:42,640
is left in his family.

85
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,960
The Empress Dowager showed mercy

86
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,680
and wanted to pardon her.

87
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,120
But this old lady

88
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,360
went to the Ministry of Justice

89
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,400
to stage a sit-in,

90
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,960
insisting on seeking justice.

91
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:53,000
She's been sitting for a day and a night.

92
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,120
Just think, who would

93
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,360
dare to take it on?

94
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,720
Do you want to die?

95
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,160
I have to die sooner or later.

96
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,400
Anyway, I can only die once.

97
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:09,440
Old lady, please stand up first.

98
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,520
If there is really an injustice,

99
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:13,280
we will certainly give you an explanation.

100
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,120
Thank you.

101
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,160
Who had the nerve

102
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:37,560
to take that old lady's case?

103
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,480
Come on, step forward.

104
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:42,280
I'm in a good mood today.
I promise I won't beat you to death.

105
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:45,120
Who took her case?

106
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,640
That old lady at the gate?

107
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:49,200
I've already sent her home.

108
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,160
Dismissed.

109
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:58,280
Go, dismissed.

110
00:06:01,092 --> 00:06:04,202
[Feng Gui]

111
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,200
Why is it you again?

112
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,440
Actually, that old lady

113
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:19,120
should be properly consoled.

114
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,640
Otherwise, she'll keep sitting at the gate

115
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:22,640
of the Ministry of Justice.

116
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:33,320
Regarding the case of Chen Baiyi,
I have already taken it very seriously…

117
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:35,920
The follow-up of this case is handed over to…

118
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:39,400
Feng Gui.

119
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:42,840
Keep an eye on that old lady,
don't let her come again.

120
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:45,240
I'll pass.

121
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,160
Director Wu, I think…

122
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,880
Come here.

123
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:59,320
The murder case of Liang Chenzhong
from the Liang Mansion

124
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,120
has been taken over by the Imperial Guards.

125
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,280
Everyone,

126
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,400
stay out of it.

127
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,560
The Imperial Guards

128
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:16,600
is not something you can interfere at will.

129
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,840
If anyone doesn't obey,

130
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:20,200
I will punish him severely.

131
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:22,400
Yes.

132
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,600
Go get busy.

133
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:30,000
Director Wu, I…

134
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,320
Yan Xing.

135
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:34,600
Chuichui.

136
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,720
Don't you two still have case files

137
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,200
to organize?

138
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,600
Go for it.

139
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,040
I…

140
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,280
Liuniang.

141
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:42,400
I suddenly remembered

142
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:45,720
that Great Chief Shen invited you to lunch.

143
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,360
It's late now.

144
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,720
Well, it's not urgent.

145
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,360
You can go have lunch.

146
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,480
Go have lunch.

147
00:07:57,880 --> 00:08:00,168
Let's go.

148
00:08:01,474 --> 00:08:03,000
[Tongming Hall]

149
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,800
Don't care about your small business.

150
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,920
- Follow me.
- Okay.

151
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,160
Then I'll follow you.

152
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,326
Sorry, you can't get in.

153
00:08:10,326 --> 00:08:12,634
[Ministry of Justice]

154
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,760
Tongming Hall has rules

155
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,920
that only male guests are accepted.

156
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,000
No female guests are allowed.

157
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,440
We are not guests.

158
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:20,520
We are here to investigate on a case.

159
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,680
Well,

160
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:25,320
send a male official here to investigate.

161
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,800
I am a clerk,

162
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,920
but she is a dignified
ninth-rank recording official

163
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,400
recorded by the Ministry of Justice.

164
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,679
If you block us,

165
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,679
maybe

166
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,320
you are objecting to the government's system

167
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,400
of selecting officials.

168
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,120
Please don't make it difficult for me.

169
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,280
If today we allow you two

170
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,360
to get in,

171
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,919
I'm afraid

172
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:45,039
I would be fired.

173
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,920
Well,

174
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:53,320
take another careful look

175
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,160
if we are male guests

176
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,520
or female guests.

177
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,560
Male guests. Please come in.

178
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:10,600
[Owner of Tongming Hall, Rong Zhui]
How could Zhanxin be so miserable?

179
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,720
I thought that

180
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:14,360
she can be a wife to Liang Chenzhong

181
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,400
and form a happy family.

182
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,720
Who would be that cruel

183
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,960
to kill her?

184
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,040
Please calm down.

185
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,760
Do you remember it?

186
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:32,640
Before Kuang Zhanxin went missing,

187
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:35,680
did anything unusual happened?

188
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,840
Or,

189
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:39,680
did she ever have a dispute with someone?

190
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:41,960
Zhanxin has always been gentle,

191
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,440
getting along well

192
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,240
with everyone.

193
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,680
Until the officials came to inform last night,

194
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:51,400
didn't you know that Kuang Zhanxin was missing?

195
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:54,720
She left on the seventeenth of last month

196
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:58,000
to go on an outing with Liang Chenzhong.

197
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,160
Liang Chenzhong

198
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:01,760
would take her out for fun before.

199
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:02,840
I thought this time,

200
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:05,680
she just went for a bit longer.

201
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,800
If we need further information,

202
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:10,040
we'd come and ask again.

203
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,160
Please calm down.

204
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,720
I heard that Chen Baiyi set himself on fire

205
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,640
and also set the Ming Hall on fire.

206
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:26,280
Fortunately, you drove him out early.

207
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:29,400
Dacang values much on background.

208
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:30,960
He's from a poor family,

209
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:33,480
and still wanted to become a noble.

210
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:36,080
It's ridiculous.

211
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,160
He's lucky to polish my essays

212
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,960
for me.

213
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,800
Yet he was still not content.

214
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,720
This bunch of poor scholars

215
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:47,200
just don't know what is gratefulness.

216
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,480
How dare he

217
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:52,120
to try to get the first place
in the Hongwen School literary competition!

218
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,280
- Come on, drink.
- Come on.

219
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:56,280
Liuniang.

220
00:10:57,480 --> 00:11:00,200
Let's go.

221
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:11,000
- Liuniang.
- Marshal Xu.

222
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,960
Miss Lu.

223
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:18,080
Marshal Xu, you're here
at Tongming Hall for a case?

224
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,120
It's the case

225
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,360
obtained by your husband.

226
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:25,360
I guess I shouldn't call you Liuniang anymore.

227
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:28,560
I should call you Mrs. Shen.

228
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:30,880
Marshal Xu, as always,

229
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:31,880
call me Liuniang.

230
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,440
Fine. Then from now on,

231
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,760
don't call me Marshal Xu anymore.

232
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:36,120
Call me Mr. Xu.

233
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,280
Okay, Mr. Xu.

234
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:40,480
After the matter of Kuang Zhanxin got out,

235
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,520
the owners of the shops

236
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,640
near the Pingkang Alley

237
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,120
act as if they are obsessed,

238
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,840
feeling like the ladies from their own shops

239
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,000
who have been out for a long time
and not returned

240
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,320
are missing.

241
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:50,000
There are a dozen cases already.

242
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,320
More people are missing?

243
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,560
No.

244
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:54,480
Among seventeen girls
who were reported missing,

245
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,360
fifteen have already been found.

246
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,400
And the two remaining,

247
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:59,280
are probably fine.

248
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,280
But there is one thing

249
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:03,200
I haven't decided whether to report it yet.

250
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:05,560
And then I met you here.

251
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,880
This records

252
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:10,360
[Missing Persons Case Files]
the cases of missing performers over the years.

253
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,000
Weird.

254
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,400
These performers

255
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:24,400
are not the most popular,

256
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:26,000
but all are well-versed in music and rhythm,

257
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,240
specializing in instrumental music

258
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,240
and skilled at playing the pipa.

259
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,520
Exactly.

260
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,880
It's just too coincidental.

261
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:33,480
That's why it feels suspicious.

262
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:41,120
These are the portraits of the missing women.

263
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,640
These women

264
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:53,600
all have the same flying fairy hairstyle.

265
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:03,000
Anything else?

266
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:04,680
Look.

267
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:06,080
The faces of these women

268
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,680
are different,

269
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:09,960
yet they all have something in common.

270
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,200
Especially in demeanor,

271
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,200
they are extremely similar.

272
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,480
Yes.

273
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:15,520
At first glance,

274
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:18,880
they really look similar.

275
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:22,600
I thought to hand these files
over to the Ministry of Justice,

276
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:25,440
but I don't think it's okay
to bypass the Imperial Guards.

277
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,760
Now it seems

278
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:28,520
it's best that you get it.

279
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:32,760
White Ghost surely wouldn't draw his sword
and kill his wife over this, right?

280
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:59,800
Then I shall take my leave first.

281
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,520
You swore oaths at dawn

