585
00:28:56,960 --> 00:29:01,308
Collection of essays from the Hongwen School.

586
00:29:01,308 --> 00:29:03,452
[Test Paper Four]

587
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:07,440
Hurry up.

588
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:10,440
