589
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:12,920
What on earth is going on?

590
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,880
Wait.

591
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:16,560
Wait, why are you here?

592
00:29:16,560 --> 00:29:18,560
