which place will suffer.

614
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,760
Be careful. Mind the steps.

615
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:58,200
Ruthless people,

616
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,680
merciless Buddha,

617
