641
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:07,800
No, my lord.

642
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:10,760
Make way for the Princess of Valor's carriage.

643
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:26,640
Princess of Valor.

644
00:31:33,360 --> 00:31:34,880
He looks somewhat familiar.

645
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:36,520
What is going on here?

646
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:38,520
Your Highness, please save my child.

647
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:41,000
Please save my child, Your Highness.

648
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:43,720
I've come to patrol the streets today,

649
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:45,600
