693
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,400
You two guard the door.

694
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,960
Tell me about anything
of the Great Chief promptly.

695
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:19,120
Yes.

696
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:21,640
No entry.

697
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,679
The Great Chief has instructed
that without permission,

698
00:34:24,679 --> 00:34:25,880
