00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:32,239
If you want to break in, step over me.

701
00:34:42,592 --> 00:34:44,000
Don't flip through.

702
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,440
If you flip through, I'll show no mercy.

703
00:34:47,480 --> 00:34:49,560
Stop flipping through.

704
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:51,480
If you keep flipping through,
I will take my own life.

705
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:53,679
If you want your Great Chief to die,

706
00:34:53,679 --> 00:34:56,719
then do it.

707
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:59,400
Grind the ink.

708
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,864
Grind the ink.

709
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:07,720
I hope it's not too late.

710
00:35:12,750 --> 00:35:15,508
[Great General]

711
00:35:29,102 --> 00:35:31,272
[Imperial Guards]

712
00:35:33,120 --> 00:35:35,920
Her handwriting is surprisingly
similar to that of the Great Chief.

713
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:47,360
Are you confident that this
can really save the Great Chief?

714
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:49,320
I can't guarantee it,

715
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:51,040
but we should at least give it a try.

716
00:35:51,040 --> 00:35:53,400
Perhaps it can avoid him
from severe punishment.

717
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:06,760
What are you waiting for? Hurry up!

718
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,960
I am waiting here.

719
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:11,080
Stop flipping through.

720
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,680
Empress Dowager.

721
00:36:19,680 --> 00:36:21,280
The Imperial Guards
has taken over the case for several days,

722
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:23,200
yet they haven't solved it.

723
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:25,280
Now there are rumors

724
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:28,360
saying the imperial court
is inept at selecting officials.

725
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,280
