730
00:36:40,240 --> 00:36:42,440
What you said

731
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:45,840
is exactly what I am concerned about.

732
00:36:47,720 --> 00:36:50,320
Shen Du from the Imperial Guards has arrived.

733
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:06,280
Shen Du,
the Great Chief of the Imperial Guards.

734
00:37:06,280 --> 00:37:08,040
Greetings to you, Empress Dowager.

735
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:10,960
May you live for long.

736
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:12,960
Minister Shen.

737
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,880
The case of the Liang family

738
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,480
has yet to be solved.

739
00:37:16,480 --> 00:37:19,480
Maybe you should give me an explanation.

740
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:20,800
Empress Dowager,

741
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,760
the murder case of the Liang family
