743
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,680
in succession at Ximing Temple

744
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:27,120
and committed by the same murderer.

745
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:28,640
Based on the evidence, the Imperial Guards

746
00:37:28,640 --> 00:37:30,200
has speeded up solving the cases.

747
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:33,280
