Then I will

754
00:37:48,600 --> 00:37:50,080
recite this nursery rhyme

755
00:37:50,080 --> 00:37:52,800
to you.

756
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:56,240
Ruthless people,

757
00:37:56,240 --> 00:37:58,320
merciless Buddha,

758
00:37:58,320 --> 00:38:00,920
under the sovereign, the order is in chaos.

759
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:04,400
Merciless Buddha hides the sin.

760
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,840
Ridiculous!

761
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:07,280
Empress Dowager, please calm down.

762
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,480
I believe that the spread of this nursery rhyme

763
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:10,640
is all because the murder case at Ximing Temple

764
00:38:10,640 --> 00:38:11,960
remains unresolved.

765
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:14,280
If the Imperial Guards
cannot find the murderer,

766
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,400
then we might as well

767
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:17,960
have an exorcism.

768
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:20,440
Empress Dowager, you are admired by all.
Don't mind

769
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:23,120
these reckless words.

770
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:32,400
Great Chief Shen.

771
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:34,520
