772
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:48,680
The Imperial Guards
suddenly arrived to arrest me,

773
00:38:48,680 --> 00:38:50,400
and I was in the process
of sorting out the case,

774
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:53,040
wanting to present it to you.

775
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:10,400
In the peaceful world,
only the Buddha's heart prevails.

776
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:13,880
Evil thoughts through countless calamities
shall never survive.

777
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:17,320
Unraveling the threads
to cleanse the grievances.

778
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:21,080
With keen insight, the world is at peace.

779
00:39:21,840 --> 00:39:23,040
Very well.

780
00:39:23,040 --> 00:39:26,120
Now that you've got clues

781
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,760
about the Liang family

782
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:29,400
and Ximing Temple.

783
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:31,600
Then let's proceed.

784
00:39:32,600 --> 00:39:35,680
Understood.

785
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:39,280
Minister Shen.

786
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:42,080
You also mentioned in your memorial

787
00:39:42,080 --> 00:39:45,040
there is an inside story
on the Ming Hall self-immolation case.

788
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:49,240
The self-immolator did not
do it to vent dissatisfaction,

789
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:52,560
but rather used death
to express his determination

790
00:39:52,560 --> 00:39:54,960
to me.

791
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:56,720
Is that true?

792
00:39:56,720 --> 00:39:58,240
I am reviewing it

793
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:00,520
and will report as soon as possible.

794
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,720
Empress Dowager.

795
00:40:02,720 --> 00:40:04,440
Alright.

796
00:40:04,440 --> 00:40:05,760
You two

797
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:08,360
are both my right-hand men.

798
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:10,640
Each with your own merits.

799
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:18,120
Enough for today, you may all leave now.

800
00:40:25,760 --> 00:40:27,880
Minister Shen.

801
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:31,600
Please stay.

802
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:35,240
I have another matter

803
00:40:35,240 --> 00:40:39,840
